         <p>Professional papers are at Alan Mason Chesney Medical Archives, Johns Hopkins University.</p>
         <p> Caroline Bedell Thomas is also featured in the National Library of Medicine's exhibit, <extref href="http://www.nlm.nih.gov/changingthefaceofmedicine/physicians/biography_317.html">Changing the Face of Medicine</extref>.</p>  
